<!--
  Hardened Runtime entitlements for the Developer ID (notarized, non-sandboxed)
  macOS build. Referenced from tauri.conf.json (bundle.macOS.entitlements);
  hardenedRuntime is true by default in Tauri v2.

  The release builder signs every bundled Mach-O with the same Developer ID
  Team ID before signing this app. The app process itself does not JIT and must
  not carry runtime exceptions. The separately spawned Node runtime receives
  its own minimal allow-jit entitlement from node-entitlements.plist.

  We deliberately do NOT enable App Sandbox or keychain-access-groups: this is a
  Developer ID app, not a sandboxed App Store app, so it reaches the system
  keychain (BYOK secret store) without a keychain entitlement, and sandboxing
  would block the loopback servers and local model/data directories.
-->
